                },
                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Grampa Sizzle fails or critically fails an attack roll or a skill check</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Grampa Sizzle makes a quick scene out of his failure, such as by falling and suddenly bouncing back to his feet or making a ridiculous face. If he has a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Laughing Fit] spell available, he can cast it as part of this reaction.</p>"
                },
